Subject: [PATCH] Add LinkedIn newsletter metrics, TJ Ads tab (Google + Meta)

- Newsletter & Pod tab: added Impressions, Members Reached, Views
  for LinkedIn Newsletter (TJP05/06/07), grouped with section headers
- New Ads tab: Google Ads (clicks, impressions, CTR, cost) and
  Meta Ads (CPC, cost, impressions, reach) stored in ads JSONB column
- Ads column requires DB migration: ALTER TABLE tj_weekly_data ADD COLUMN ads jsonb

